{"url": "https://boingboing.net/tag/not-food/page/2", "text": "The mystery of the glorious fireball emitted by microwaved grapes (featured in my novel Little Brother) has been resolved, thanks to a paper in the Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences in which Trent University researchers Hamza Khattak and Aaron Slepkov explain how they destroyed a dozen microwaves before figuring out that the grapes were just the right size and had enough humidity to set up standing waves that amplify the microwaves -- and anything roughly grape-sized will do the same. Read the rest", "images": ["https://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-QX6JKE-6M4Jf7.gif", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/view.jpeg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/bananacandle02.jpg", "https://s0.wp.com/i/blank.jpg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/800px-Injera.jpg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/35886096_1547590756936324_r.jpeg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/DqxLVurWwAAPBCp.jpg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/turnspit-dog_dogwheel-at-st.-briarvel-s-castle_wide-dd427ff1208e53a40d237cf72e2a569695a4a94d-s1200-c85.jpg", "https://sb.scorecardresearch.com/p?c1=2&c2=7518287&cv=2.0&cj=1", "https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=1174428159312267&ev=PageView&noscript=1", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/29064927963_94819ae7b7_k.jpg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hero.jpg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/2163450054_1094ac3df5_b-750x507.jpg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/animation-1-1.gif", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/themes/bng/i/logo.png", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/tumblr_inline_pkxt3qzC1B1sppt0x_1280.png", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Dt282aiVsAEZ5mC.jpg", "https://media.boingboing.net/wp-content/up